{
  "stem": "21731.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I decided to visit Max and my mother in Lwow for a weekend or for a few days, and then come back to Warsaw and see what's going on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "While I was in in Lwow, Max got his call-up papers because he was in the reserve-- a captain in the reserve.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was the end of our dreams.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Also, we thought that there won't be a war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was just called up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I wanted to have Jan with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And civilians were not allowed to travel anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The trains were all taken up by the services.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Jan, Jan-- Max went to fetch Jan, brought him back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As-- the child was standing in, in shorts, and the little shirts, or whatever he had, sandals-- just grabbed him and came back to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed with my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Max had to go back to his [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] unit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 17th of September, the Russian moved into, into Lwow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My husband was already gone with his unit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was with my mother and Jan in my mother's flat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the Russian-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in-- I thought it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But later, in comparison with the Germans, they were angels for us, not for other people who were killed in, in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The first personal loss for us was the arrest and deportation of Victor Hyas, who was my mother-in-law's brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was the president of B'nai B'rith, the vice-- of-- the vice president of Lwow, and a banker.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was, for the Russians, enough to kill  a person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was deported and killed in Kiev after a few days in prison.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was the first personal loss for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
